The paper proposes a deep learning framework for brain decoding using long short-term memory (LSTM) recurrent neural networks (RNNs) to model the temporal dependencies in functional MRI data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories, as well as the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories, which are all relevant to deep learning and neural network modeling.
